都是咨询我，他能顺利的通过面试，而且他说里面很多员工都刚刚入行，只有一些基础。但这些人都能顺利通过面试，而我这么有经验的人却不要我，我也无语了。我是不是不要在这个行业死扛了，是不是应该转行了。没有口才，没有体力，转行做什么真不知道，其他行业对于一个40多岁的0经验的人应该都无法接受。之前面试过一个做软件维护工作，首先培训软件使用和财务知识，每天都是用电脑做题，而培训老师讲完就走，遇上问题根本不知道怎么解决。而老板每天早会都骂人，嫌我们进度慢。老板和我年龄差不多，每天当着那么多人面骂我，而且培训期间没有工资，还不属于他员工，我实在受不了就走了。但回到家里看着老婆孩子和每天家里的各种费用，我又不知道如何收入从哪里来？更不敢想象等我50岁时打工彻底该怎么办？"},"attached_info":"CkAI7JDbkb+u6IYbEAMaCTEwNTY1NzYwNSDVrNauBjAAOIIFQAdyCTY0NTIwOTk1MXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"75 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-3d917fb11613b7b13ecd7bbeb1c554e6_xl.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"8_1733232723.172341","card_id":"Q_5626786408","target":{"id":5626786408,"title":"如何看待媒体称「鹿晗为准备音乐节一天吃一顿每天跑 10km」，是否对身体造成影响？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/5626786408","type":"question","created":1733019539,"answer_count":222,"follower_count":298,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[658,833,844,108840],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"[2 张图片]"},"attached_info":"CkEI7JDbkb+u6IYbEAMaCTExMjEwMTg4NiCTj6+6BjAAOKoCQAhyCjU2MjY3ODY0MDh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"72 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-7ff81b236f91c91ccee0216c3747b464_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"9_1733232723.172754","card_id":"Q_5533738500","card_label":{"type":"new","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":5533738500,"title":"东契奇为什么在巅峰年龄，断涯式下滑呢？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/5533738500","type":"question","created":1732919387,"answer_count":17,"follower_count":23,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url